metadata.name: Deep Down in a Dream - Trapped
metadata.description:
I was a bear in my dream. Well, not the big brown bear, which lives in the woods, the dangerous one, but the pink plush breed. I sank deep into the dream, suddenly I was surrounded by wild green tendrils and didn't let me go, anyway I was trying to get rid of. I felt like I'm drowning.
Everything was like deep in the sea, but somehow different...

I wonder what does it mean?

300 dpi
